{
  "stanzas": [
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "“Forgive our sins as we forgive,”"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "You taught us, Lord, to pray;"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "But You alone can grant us grace"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "To live the words we say."
        }
      ],
      "number": 1
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "How can Your pardon reach and bless"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "The unforgiving heart"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "That broods on wrongs and will not let"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "Old bitterness depart?"
        }
      ],
      "number": 2
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "In blazing light Your cross reveals"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "The truth we dimly knew:"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "How trifling others’ debts to us;"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "How great our debt to You!"
        }
      ],
      "number": 3
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "Lord, cleanse the depths within our souls"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "And bid resentment cease;"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "Then, by Your mercy reconciled,"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "Our lives will spread Your peace."
        }
      ],
      "number": 4
    }
  ],
  "title": "Forgive Our Sins as We Forgive"
}
